      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest possible standard. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior, looks and feels brand new. The engine and transmission perform perfectly, and all mechanical components are in peak condition with no signs of wear. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that is indistinguishable from its original factory state.",
