    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for over the years. Perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that still looks great on the road! I\u2019ve loved every mile in this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
      "price": 31500.0,
